                <mxCell id="legend" value="&lt;b&gt;Auth (same JWT secret, different claims)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Admin: POST /auth/login → org-scoped API&lt;br&gt;• Tenant: POST /tenant/auth/login → /tenant/me, /tenant/leases&lt;br&gt;• Platform: POST /auth/login (isPlatformAdmin) → /platform/*&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Dev:&lt;/b&gt; Vite proxy VITE_API_URL=/api → http://localhost:3000" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fontSize=11;fontColor=#0F0202;" parent="1" vertex="1">
